response.original_title: WASHINGTON DC TRUCK STOP - THE FILM
response.overview: To do it all over again.  Washington DC Truck Stop - The Film is the story of Truck's 2023 effort to raising the legendary USAU Club National Championship Trophy. This is to many friends, old and new, who were able to accomplish one of the greatest feats in our sport over years and years of dedication.
response.tagline: To do it all over again.
